      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"5. MEISHO TABIZUKI raced in the leading division and kept going to score by half a length last time out over 1600m at this track. Meeting a deeper field this time but he deserves plenty of thought. 2. COSMO MAGALLANICA kicked off this campaign with a win two runs ago. Couldn't follow that up last time out when second over 1600m at this track, beaten 0.8 lengths. Finds a tougher race but he has the talent to test this line-up. 8. MUMTY PRINCE booted up from a low draw to lead last start and went on to score by a nose at this track over 1650m. Expected to feature. 3. REAL SAFARI has been in the placings at her last two starts, finishing third last time over 1600m at this track. Suitably placed so anticipating another big run.\",\"runners\":[5,2,8,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
